title: IN PICTURES: SA wet, wet, wet
text:
A week after tropical storm Dineo threatened to wreak havoc in South Africa, parts of Gauteng, Mpumalanga and the North West have experienced flooding. 
Here is a look at some pictures that were posted to twitter on Tuesday: There is now a lake where the lawn used to be...garage looks like it's floating #flooding #rain #SouthAfrica pic.twitter.com/VIktobT67G â€” TY BAXTER (@mrtybaxter) February 21, 2017 Wolmaransstad flooding in SA today pic.twitter.com/MuybcIA1gS
